5000|$|Who Am I? {{was shot}} on {{locations}} in Namibia, South Africa, and Netherlands between February and March 1997. The film features several landmarks such as Sun City in South Africa, Erasmus Bridge in Rotterdam, the Beurstraverse (which was portrayed {{by the film}} makers as being in Johannesburg), the Cube houses and the Willemswerf building (which served as {{the headquarters of the}} villains and from the side of which, [...] "Who Am I?" [...] <b>escaped</b> by <b>sliding</b> to the ground).|$|R
